snippet.title: SOMA - E3 2015 Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
SOMA is a sci-fi horror game from Frictional Games, creators of the groundbreaking Amnesia and Penumbra series.

Out now on PC and PS4.

Buy now at Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/282140/
GOG:
https://www.gog.com/game/soma
or on PSN

For more information, visit:
http://www.SomaGame.com
